Package com.restfb.types.send.media

Class MediaTemplateUrlElement

java.lang.Object
com.restfb.types.AbstractFacebookType
com.restfb.types.send.media.MediaTemplateUrlElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
MediaAttachment.MediaTemplateElement, Serializable
public class MediaTemplateUrlElement
extends AbstractFacebookType
implements MediaAttachment.MediaTemplateElement
Represents the media template element that is used with the url as defined here Allowed urls are:
  • https://business.facebook.com//videos/
  • https://www.facebook.com//videos//
  • https://business.facebook.com//photos/
  • https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=
